# - Try to find Jack
# Once done this will define
#
#  JACK_FOUND - system has Jack
#  JACK_INCLUDE_DIRS - the Jack include directory
#  JACK_LIBRARIES - Link these to use Jack
#  JACK_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using Jack
